              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Neutron multiscaling curves(NMC) and beta multiscaling",
                "curves (BMC) were produced. NMC had one component,",
                "excluding mass 98 (Sr, Y) .",
                "BMC were fitted to exp.points using previously",
                "measured or estimated Pn as trial value. By iteration",
                "of Pn the intensity of precursor component of BMC was",
                "obtained.",
                "  Pn value was determined from the ratio of neutron and",
                "beta intensities In, Ibeta and detection efficiencies",
                "EPSbeta, EPSn ratio :",
                "  Pn=(In/Ibeta)*(EPSbeta/EPSn)",
                "Ratio EPSbeta/EPSn was determined by the previously",
                "measured Pn for Li-9 ( see REL-REF Y.S.Chen+) and",
                "In/Ibeta for Li-9 measured at this experiment."
              ]
            }
          ],
